Bio-Community version 0.01
==========================

Bio::Community is a BioPerl-based module to represent and manipulate communities
of organisms. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Moose

